Metadata-Version: 1.0
Name: stroller
Version: 0.3.1
Summary: E-commerce module library for Turbogears
Home-page: http://projects.axantlabs.com/Stroller
Author: AXANT
Author-email: tech@axant.it
License: GPL
Description: Stroller is a indipendent module that integrates a full customizable e-commerce section under your /shop route.
        The main features are:
          * Paypal payments
          * Goods categories
          * Barcodes and SKU management
          * Anonymous checkouts
          * Fully themable
          * Purchase Orders
          * Invoicing
          * Shipping time management
          * Fully l10n and i18n
        
        Easy to use it is as easy as be imported.
        
Keywords: turbogears2 turbogears2.extension ecommerce paypal shop lib
Platform: UNKNOWN
